{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b2d6361f34","title":"在中央工作会议上的插话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a197c9fbd9","index":0,"year":1964,"month":12,"day":15,"articleId":"b2d6361f34"}],"tags":[{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji47","name":"毛泽东全集第47卷","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/47-OCR.pdf"},{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁(1961-1968卷)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji47":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"42fc3d8733","type":"title","text":"在中央工作会议上的插话","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"3b6ac2da0a","type":"paragraph","text":"（有些地方提出，出现了新生的资产阶级分子。）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"4fe9a01b74","type":"paragraph","text":"叫新生资产阶级分子，农民不容易懂，还是叫贪污盗窃、投机到把分子好，农民懂得。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"a541696dfe","type":"paragraph","text":"（加强社教工作队的领导问题。战线是不是要缩短些？","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"151f93cbe1","type":"paragraph","text":"要短容易，收缩嘛！","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"b1acec91cc","type":"paragraph","text":"（关于农村整党、建党问题","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"800871ceb2","type":"paragraph","text":"我早就赞成。…....","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"8c53b02253","type":"paragraph","text":"（要发展一批党员）","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"865b75db15","type":"paragraph","text":"还是从贫下中农、工人积极分子中去发展党员。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"851ebee49b","type":"paragraph","text":"（下边借反资本主义来反对贫下中农。","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"b2e43c9b3e","type":"paragraph","text":"让他搞嘛！你不让他搞，他慈不住。要反群众，他就暴露出来了。题。）（机关干部家属中有不少四类分子，要清理。这是个普遍的问","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"1195ab5cad","type":"paragraph","text":"反革命、恶霸、四类分子，就那么多嘛！几千万，几百方，分散各地，总是少数。只有那么多，有是有，清是要清，多是不多。","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"650722b00f","type":"paragraph","text":"（领导于部膜点，还是增在大队的好。","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"bfb93d23c9","type":"paragraph","text":"抓中间，吃两头","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"ea602e8b39","type":"paragraph","text":"（这次社教运动中，有些地方还查出不少黑地。","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"4973449be3","type":"paragraph","text":"我看腾百分之二十至三十就算好的","index":15,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"f9d6c5d40f","type":"paragraph","text":"（我看查出来，过三五年再征购。）","index":16,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"67613c8b29","type":"paragraph","text":"粮食五年到十年不征购，以后增产再增购一些。粮食还是存在老百姓家里好，否则，阻止人家报黑地","index":17,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"9a7852db59","type":"paragraph","text":"（要把干部不脱离生产的制度固定下来。）","index":18,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"4273d33672","type":"paragraph","text":"反官像主义，要跟班生产。","index":19,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"ea6fd493a0","type":"paragraph","text":"（科室人员有半天的工作时间也就够了。","index":20,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"66208aa23c","type":"paragraph","text":"还要注意文牌主义。","index":21,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"5186aceadb","type":"paragraph","text":"能够四、五小时劳动，厂长、党委书记事就少了，开会、文件也会少了，工作就能做好了。","index":22,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"0a22e3dafb","type":"paragraph","text":"（会议结束时）我们的会议，每天下午三点半开大会，大家可以在大会上发言。上午开小会。你们如果秘密谈，出简报我也不看。你们要畅所欲言，冲口而出。讲的不对，有什么要紧？大家可以原谅嘛！","index":23,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"b2d6361f34"}],"page":{"id":"f5ff512e0d","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"b2d6361f34","start":315,"end":316}},"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"03a41bf2e3","type":"paragraph","text":"我看瞒百分之二十——三十就算好的。","index":17,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"12e95b30fe","type":"paragraph","text":"〔要发展一批党员〕","index":8,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"135aba1f7f","type":"paragraph","text":"〔领导干部蹲点，还是蹲在大队的好。〕","index":14,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"1d0b07e1e6","type":"paragraph","text":"能够四、五小时劳动，厂长、党委书记事就少了，开会、文件也会少了，工作就能做好了。","index":23,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"1d113016d1","type":"title","text":"在中央工作会议上的插话","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"2898d9aea0","type":"paragraph","text":"反革命、恶霸、四类分子，就那么多嘛！几千万，几百万，分散各地，总是少数。只有那么多，有是有，清是要清，多是不多。","index":13,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"2a30331806","type":"paragraph","text":"要短容易，收缩嘛！","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"2f5d5a33bb","type":"paragraph","text":"〔这次社教运动中，有些地方还查出不少黑地。〕","index":16,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"3d5c356050","type":"paragraph","text":"〔下边借反资本主义来反对贫下中农〕","index":10,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"43116fc10b","type":"paragraph","text":"还是从贫下中农、工人积极分子中去发展党。","index":9,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"44fbb7e1f0","type":"paragraph","text":"叫新生资产阶级分子，农民不容易懂，还是叫贪污盗窃、投机倒把分子好，农民懂得。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"4858f0d2eb","type":"paragraph","text":"〔关于农村整党、建党问题〕","index":6,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"52cd24b8ce","type":"paragraph","text":"抓中间，吃两头。","index":15,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"55de20ec01","type":"paragraph","text":"让他搞嘛！你不让他搞，他憋不住。要反群众，他就暴露出来了。","index":11,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"5b13296f06","type":"paragraph","text":"（会议结束时）我们的会议，每天下午三点半开大会，大家可以在大会上发言。上午开小会。你们如果秘密谈，出简报我也不看。你们要畅所欲言，冲口而出。讲的不对，有什么要紧？大家可以原谅嘛！","index":24,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"5bd18e749d","type":"paragraph","text":"〔我看查出来，过三、五年再征购。〕粮食五年到十年不征购，以后增产再增购一些。粮食还是存在老百姓家里好，否则，阻止人家报黑地。","index":18,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"5d149ecd37","type":"paragraph","text":"我早就赞成。......","index":7,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"686b4ee127","type":"paragraph","text":"反官僚主义，要跟班生产。","index":20,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"873b6f5e1f","type":"paragraph","text":"〔要把干部不脱离生产的制度固定下来。〕","index":19,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"8838404c59","type":"paragraph","text":"〔有些地方提出，出现了新生的资产阶级分子。〕","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"9a478bed9f","type":"paragraph","text":"〔科室人员有半天的工作时间也就够了。〕","index":21,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"a53aa06b4e","type":"paragraph","text":"（注：方括号内为刘××讲话的有关内容）","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"a92e06f76b","type":"paragraph","text":"〔加强社教工作队的领导问题。战线是不是要缩短些？〕","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"cfc996b94e","type":"paragraph","text":"〔机关干部家属中有不少四类分子，要清理。这是个普遍的问题。〕","index":12,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"b2d6361f34"},{"id":"d77fda2cf9","type":"paragraph","text":"还要注意文牍主义。","index":22,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"b2d6361f34"}],"page":{"id":"b84f8fad68","publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"b2d6361f34","start":365,"end":366}}}},"__N_SSG":true}